name: the man with the murder mansion
description:
creative thinker #2
Herman Webster Mudgett; the man, the myth, the ladies call him H.H. Holmes. Mr. Holmes brought his dreams to life by building the beautiful World's Fair Hotel. My stay there was very enjoyable. My only complaint is that the lady occupying the room under me would not stop screaming for help. Thankfully, after 20 minutes the screams subsided.
